rComments: Most of the course is very straight forward, similar to what you would see in general high school business courses. His online written assignments are marked fairly tough. Most of the exam is based on his lecture slides, an definitions from the textbook. He tells real life stories during his lectures based on his life experiences which are funny
Hard course, be prepared for it.
